General.Name: Wallenstam AB (publ)
General.Description: Wallenstam AB (publ) develops, builds, manages, and sells residential and commercial properties for people and companies in Sweden. The company's property portfolio comprises apartments with commercial tenants. It also owns and operates 53 wind turbines with a total installed output of 112 megawatts. Wallenstam AB (publ) was founded in 1944 and is headquartered in Gothenburg, Sweden.
